VIDEO | Mumbai: On Hindi language row, Congress leader Vijay Wadettiwar (
@VijayWadettiwar
) says, “We are against ‘Hindi Shakti’. Our mother tongue is Marathi and learning any other language over this should be a choice. This is our issue, and we discussed it with state party president. We are ready to protest.”

#Maharashtra 

(Full video available on PTI Videos - 
ptivideos.com)
